{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":16.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_01","textHome":"我们龙城家，是自江户时期起代代延续的武士@家族，也是剑派「龙真流」的本家。除了剑术，@龙真流还教授枪术和小太刀术等等，是一个@综合性流派，我学习的是长刀术，@正以出师为目标，日益精进！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_18","textHome":"第三式为「升龙」！@将刀刃对准敌人架在上路。@如画圈一般从下方向上挑击，@便是「升龙圆月斩」！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_19","textHome":"我做到了！眼前的阻碍已被我一刀两断！@我，还能变得更强！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":100}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_20","textHome":"不要慌……不要慌……静下心来……@呼~看到了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_21","textHome":"精神的修行也不可欠缺。那就要打坐！@盘腿而坐，深呼吸……慢慢地……慢慢地……@慢……啊！我才没有睡着！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":200}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_22","textHome":"为了让感觉更敏锐，我正在绝食中……。@现在我的大脑十分清晰。@我完全没有在想食物的事情！@烤肉寿司炸虾拉面牛肉饼……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":101300,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_23","textHome":"摈除杂念最好的办法就是瀑布修行！不过我没@找到合适的瀑布……所以，我在家里建了一个@「私人瀑布」！……喂，父亲大人等等！不要用@我的瀑布洗头啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.6,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_24","textHome":"又见面了呢。所谓「士别三日当刮目相待」，@魔法少女又该是如何呢？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":300}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_25","textHome":"在晨练结束后，我会用抹布来打扫道场，@打扫完之后真的感觉很清爽！@清晨干净的道场……真是眼福啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":101300,"motion":100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_26","textHome":"这是我们家族在战场上食用的「龙城饼」！@是便于携带的硬饼，裹上一些草就能食用的@便餐。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_27","textHome":"今天就直接回家学习和训练……诶？@有卖好吃的奶油年糕小豆粥的店？……@那我暂且去确认一下位置吧……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":101300,"motion":0}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_03","textHome":"呜呜……美凪肯定又是在耍我！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_28","textHome":"训练出了一身汗之后，悠闲地泡个澡然后进入@梦乡……这样子真是太舒服了！@是每天都不可欠缺的流程呢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":200}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_29","textHome":"光阴似箭！@时间总是过得那么快，今天也已成过去。@所以，清清楚楚，堂堂正正地做人吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":100}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_30","textHome":"怎么会这样……万万没想到……@不能放任不管……@必须……必须要做些什么！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":101300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":100}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_31","textHome":"想和我比试吗？@那么……那就做好相应的觉悟吧！@我是不会手软的！来吧来吧来吧！@一决胜负~！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":100}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_32","textHome":"嗯嗯嗯！这便是一场合战！@那么，就交给我来打头阵吧！@上吧上吧~！堂堂正正战斗吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":100}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_33","textHome":"我忍受不了画框歪了，桌子没排整齐这些事！@我马上就去把它们弄整齐！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":100}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_34","textHome":"龙真流的长刀术，是以实战为设想磨砺出来的@刀法。是不会落后于枪剑之类的武器的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_35","textHome":"武道最基本的就是礼。以礼开始以礼结束。@平常也要将礼铭记在心！@那么，……行正面礼！行老师礼！相互行礼！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":100}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_36","textHome":"我推荐大家去学习武道！@保证大家精神方面能获得巨大成长！……@顺便，我们道场现在正招收弟子！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101300}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_37","textHome":"祖先大人过去在水名城担任剑术指导，@以训练严厉闻名！……@不过，也是因为这个的原因被解职了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_04","textHome":"虽然很不想用这招……但没有办法了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_38","textHome":"深月真是个随心所欲的人。而且非常散漫！@哪一天我要把礼仪举止和行为修养彻底地@传授给她！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_39","textHome":"我的表兄是个优秀的警官，@同时也是我们道场优秀的前辈。@剑法在我们流派也是首屈一指！@有机会的话还想请他赐教。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_40","textHome":"常盘……那位小姐也出生在传统家庭，@是一位端庄美丽的人……@然而，她却有种微妙的可怕感，@或者说是压迫感……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":100}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_41","textHome":"这个吗？哼哼……这是洋装！是在神滨有名的@精品店买的！怎么样？这件很新潮吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101300}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_42","textHome":"来吧，正面对决！"}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_43","textHome":"胜利，我收下了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101300}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_44","textHome":"这便是龙真流！"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_45","textHome":"越是胜利越要警惕……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101300}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_46","textHome":"那么，高呼胜利吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_63","textHome":"这就是龙真流的奥义！龙真闪光爪牙！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":200}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_05","textHome":"我发誓要以这事为教训，好好锻炼记忆力……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":100}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_64","textHome":"我要从正中斩断你！"}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_65","textHome":"好好见识我流派的精髓吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":200}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_66","textHome":"乾坤一掷！咿呀啊啊啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"id":101300,"motion":200}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_02","textHome":"呀呀！远而听声，近而见型！@我乃龙真流长刀术代理门主，@龙城明日香，在此见过！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":101300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":101300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1013_00_13","textHome":"只有通过修行才能领悟奥义！@千里之行始于足下！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":101300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":100}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFi